#1. change
hostnamectl set-hostname client.test.com

#2. check
hostnamectl status

#3. Close the current session and relaunch the terminal

Hostname can be:
  * 64 character in a length
  * Recommend to have FQDN
  * Consists of a-z, A-Z, 0-9, “-”, “_” and “.” only
  
source: https://www.itzgeek.com/how-tos/linux/centos-how-tos/change-hostname-in-centos-7-rhel-7.html  
